23 SECTION 11. A new section to chapter 54-60 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
24 and enacted as follows:
25 Reporting requirements - Budget section - Grant programs.
26 The department shall compile a report regarding grant programs administered by the
27 department, excluding federally funded programs, to be provided semiannually to the budget
28 section. The report must include the following for each grant program:
29 1. The purpose of the grant program;
30 2. Funding history;
31 3. The number of days the grant application was open to applicants;
