3 SECTION 12. AMENDMENT. Section 54-60-31 of the North Dakota Century Code is
4 amended and reenacted as follows:
5 54-60-31. Office of legal immigrationglobal talent - Duties.
6 There is created an office of legal immigrationglobal talent within the department of
7 commerce. Employees of the office of legal immigrationglobal talent report to the commissioner.
8 The office of legal immigrationglobal talent:
9 1. Shall develop and implement a statewide strategy to support businesses in recruiting
10 and retaining foreign labor, including immigrants already in the United States and
11 integration of immigrants into the state to promote economic opportunities for
12 immigrant communities.
13 2. Shall advise and make recommendations to the governor, legislative assembly, and
14 state agencies regarding immigrant integration and foreign labor issues.
15 3. Shall develop a pilot program to support businesses pursuing or employing legal
16 immigrants and to support communities to develop immigration integration plans and
17 activities.
18 4. May contract with other state agencies to develop and administer programs or
19 services related to immigration integration and access to basic needs that promote
20 entrance and movement throughout the workforce.
21 5. May contract with an organization with expertise related to the goals of the office of
22 legal immigrationglobal talent.
